                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8817" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0085</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2252 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“绿富同兴”到“环环相扣”:恒瑞环科企业内循环链入循环经济产业链之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;Green Prosperity and Prosperity Together&quot; to &quot;Interoperability&quot;: The Road for Hengrui Environmental Science and Technology Enterprises to Enter the Circular Economy Industry Chain through Internal Circulation Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王科唯，张寅，董爱荷，高平，刘永团（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古鄂尔多斯市恒瑞环科制造有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">环保部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恒瑞环科；生物质能；大小循环经济；产业链</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hengrui Environmental Science; Biomass energy; Small and large circular economy; Industrial chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自2004年我国提出农林生物质工程国家战略以来，生物质能产业发展逐渐呈现种类齐全、资源量大、政策完善、产业体系完整的向好态势。然而，以企业“小循环”链入产业“大循环”的双循环发展体系的构建仍然是我国生物质能产业发展所面临的难题。本案例阐述了在“两链”融合、“两化”融合发展的背景下，恒瑞环科通过高效利用当地丰富的沙柳等生物质资源，创造性地提出“资源建链-技术补链-市场延链-组织强链”的企业内小循环经济产业链模式，并逐步链入到生物质能大循环经济产业链中，形成企业内“小循环”到产业内“大循环”的融会贯通，打破产业链之间的时间和空间限制并进行资源高效利用，确保生物质能循环经济产业链的正常运转。该案例在为沙漠治理行业的生物质能开发利用提供借鉴和参考的同时，旨在引导学生探索企业小循环与产业大循环的内在联系，理解和掌握构建循环经济产业链在生物质能发展中的重要作用和意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since China proposed the national strategy of agricultural and forestry biomass engineering in 2004, the development of biomass energy industry has gradually shown a positive trend of complete types, large resources, sound policies, and complete industrial system. However, the construction of a dual cycle development system that integrates the &quot;small cycle&quot; of enterprises into the &quot;big cycle&quot; of industries remains a challenge for the development of China&#39;s biomass energy industry. This case illustrates that in the context of the integration of &quot;two chains&quot; and &quot;two transformations&quot;, Hengrui Environmental Science and Technology has creatively proposed a small circular economy industry chain model within the enterprise through efficient utilization of local abundant biomass resources such as willows, such as &quot;resource construction chain, technology supplement chain, market extension chain, and organizational strong chain&quot;, and gradually integrated it into the biomass energy large circular economy industry chain, forming a seamless integration from the &quot;small cycle&quot; within the enterprise to the &quot;large cycle&quot; within the industry, breaking the time and space limitations between industry chains and carrying out efficient resource utilization, ensuring the normal operation of the biomass energy circular economy industry chain. This case aims to provide reference and inspiration for the development and utilization of biomass energy in the desert management industry, while guiding students to explore the internal connection between enterprise small cycle and industrial large cycle, and to understand and master the important role and significance of building a circular economy industry chain in the development of biomass energy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《循环经济学》、《产业经济学》、《管理经济学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">循环经济产业链的内涵和和特征；循环经济产业链的原则；循环经济产业链的构建；纵向一体化；产业升级；技术创新战略；产业链；创新链</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
